  <description type="morphology">Corm coat heavily fibrous. Scape 5–25 cm. Flowers: perianth bluish violet or bluish purple, tube 6–13 cm, lobes 15–25 mm; anther apex hooked; staminodia white; ovary 8–9 mm; style 9–11 mm. 2n = 12, 24, 42.</description>
